Here's tips, if you want to change clock of airflow webserver page.
@haitaoyao I hope this tip can be helpful to you. :)
- the left side of header : clock
  - /usr/local/lib/python2.7/site-packages/airflow/www/templates/admin/base.html

```
    <script>
 81         x = new Date()
 82         //var UTCseconds = (x.getTime() + x.getTimezoneOffset()*60*1000);
 83         var seconds = x.getTime();
 84         $("#clock").clock({
 85             "seconds":"false",
 86             "calendar":"false",
 87             "format":"24",
 88             "timestamp":seconds
 89         }).click(function(){
 90             alert('{{ hostname }}');
 91         });
 92     </script>
```
